	<section class = "container-fluid">
	<h2>Creating "What Does Supply and Demand Mean."</h2>
	</section>
	
	<section class = "container-fluid">
	<p>This video was created from a question I constantly ask myself: “What does supply and demand mean for me—the consumer.”</p>

<p class = "special">In making this video:</p>

<p>First, I storyboarded all of the parts that I would use in my video. This allowed me to judge where all my text, pictures and other elements were going to go in the video. Storyboarding also allowed me get a feel for what motions I would be using in the video. Take at look at some of my panels from my storyboard.</p>

</section>

