<section class = "container-fluid">
<p>Next, I recorded the lines I had scripted out for my video.</p>

<p>After arranging the sound in Adobe After Effects, I started creating my assets in Adobe Illustrator. The cat, apple, gaming controller, and dress were all originally created by me, and all of these products—like every product produced by a business—are subjected to the laws of supply and demand.</p>

<p>Once my assets were created, I could finally arrange them in the video. I brought them to life through the use of wiggling, looping, and sound mixing.</p>

<p>This video was created with the help of motion graphics. I created and arranged all assets and backgrounds used in the video.</p>
</section>
